37681>>>>>>>>>>>>>    Procedure SetActionButtons
37684>>>>>>>>>>>>>        tWebNavigateData NavigateData
37684>>>>>>>>>>>>>        tWebNavigateData NavigateData
37684>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Boolean bHasRecord
37684>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Handle hoDD
37684>>>>>>>>>>>>>
37684>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Get Server to hoDD
37685>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Get GetNavigateData to NavigateData
37686>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Get HasRecord of hoDD to bHasRecord
37687>>>>>>>>>>>>>
37687>>>>>>>>>>>>>        // let's hide all buttons and then Show the ones we want
37687>>>>>>>>>>>>>        WebSet pbRender of oEditBtn to False
37688>>>>>>>>>>>>>        WebSet pbRender of oSaveBtn to False
37689>>>>>>>>>>>>>        WebSet pbRender of oCancelChangesBtn to False
37690>>>>>>>>>>>>>        WebSet pbRender of oDeleteBtn to False
37691>>>>>>>>>>>>>
37691>>>>>>>>>>>>>        If (NavigateData.bReadOnly) Begin
37693>>>>>>>>>>>>>            WebSet pbRender of oEditBtn to True
37694>>>>>>>>>>>>>        End
37694>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
37694>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Else Begin
37695>>>>>>>>>>>>>            WebSet pbRender of oSaveBtn to True
37696>>>>>>>>>>>>>            WebSet pbRender of oCancelChangesBtn to True
37697>>>>>>>>>>>>>            WebSet pbRender of oDeleteBtn to bHasRecord
37698>>>>>>>>>>>>>        End
37698>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
37698>>>>>>>>>>>>>    End_Procedure
37699>>>>>>>>>>>>>
37699>>>>>>>>>>>>>    Procedure OnViewSaved Handle hoServer Boolean bChanged
37702>>>>>>>>>>>>>        // Close after save
37702>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Send NavigateClose Self
37703>>>>>>>>>>>>>    End_Procedure
